---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navigation from "../components/Navigation.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro"
import CTA from "../components/CTA.astro";
---

<Layout title="Services - PJ Marketing Solutions" description="Data enrichment, televerification, email marketing, hosted buyer programmes, and on-site registration - end-to-end exhibition marketing services from PJ Marketing Solutions.">
    <section class="page-hero">
        <Navigation />
        <div class="hero-overlay">
            <h1> Services. </h1>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="services-intro">
        <h2> What we do. </h2>
        <p>With over 11 years of experience, we help sales and marketing teams build stronger pipelines and achieve their revenue and performance goals.</p>
        <p>We support your sales and marketing teams with services that include sales development, B2B telemarketing, market research, and data management. Whether you need a fully outsourced solution or support in specific areas, our programmes are tailored to your goals and built to drive measurable growth.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="service-list">

        <section class="service-split">
            <div class="service-image">
                <img src="/images/database.jpg" alt="B2B data enrichment for exhibition marketing"/>
            </div>
            <div class="text">
                <h3>Data Enrichment</h3>
                <h4>Turn raw data into actionable insights</h4>
                <p>Outdated or incomplete contact data wastes your team's time and budget. Our B2B data enrichment service appends, cleanses, and validates your existing database — adding missing job titles, company information, direct contact details, and industry classifications so your campaigns reach the right people every time.</p>
                <p>We work with exhibition organisers, associations, and corporate marketing teams across the Middle East to transform basic lists into high-performing assets. A cost-effective alternative to buying new data, and far more accurate than working with what you have.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="service-button">Get Started</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="service-split">
            <div class="service-image">
                <img src="/images/telephone.png" alt="Televerification service for event and exhibition databases"/>
            </div>
            <div class="text">
                <h3>Televerification</h3>
                <h4>Reliable data you can trust. Validated by real conversations.</h4>
                <p>Televerification is the process of phone-verifying your contact database to confirm accuracy before a campaign or event. Our agents call each record to validate job titles, decision-making authority, contact details, and continued interest — giving you a clean, qualified list you can act on with confidence.</p>
                <p>For exhibition organisers, this means knowing your invited attendees and buyers are real, reachable, and relevant before you invest in outreach. We've verified hundreds of thousands of records for events across the Middle East and Europe.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="service-button">Get Started</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="service-split">
            <div class="service-image">
                <img src="/images/email.png" alt="Email marketing campaigns for exhibitions and events"/>
            </div>
            <div class="text">
                <h3>Email Marketing</h3>
                <h4>Compelling campaigns that land, resonate, and convert.</h4>
                <p>We design and deliver targeted email campaigns for event organisers, exhibitors, and B2B marketing teams. From audience segmentation and copywriting to send scheduling and performance reporting, we manage the full campaign lifecycle so your message reaches the right inbox at the right time.</p>
                <p>Our campaigns are built around your goals — whether that's driving visitor registrations, re-engaging lapsed attendees, promoting an exhibitor package, or nurturing leads post-event. Every send is tracked, measured, and optimised.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="service-button">Get Started</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="service-split">
            <div class="service-image">
                <img src="/images/hosted.png" alt="Hosted buyer programme management for trade shows"/>
            </div>
            <div class="text">
                <h3>Hosted Buyer</h3>
                <h4>Connecting qualified buyers with the right suppliers — seamlessly.</h4>
                <p>A hosted buyer programme is only as strong as the quality of buyers you recruit. We handle the end-to-end process — identifying senior decision-makers in your target industries, qualifying them against your criteria, and securing their commitment to attend and meet with exhibitors.</p>
                <p>Our team coordinates travel, scheduling, and pre-event communication so that by the time your event opens, every hosted buyer is briefed, confirmed, and ready to do business. The result is higher ROI for exhibitors and stronger outcomes for organisers.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="service-button">Get Started</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="service-split">
            <div class="service-image">
                <img src="/images/registration.png" alt="On-site event registration and badge printing"/>
            </div>
            <div class="text">
                <h3>On-site Registration</h3>
                <h4>Fast, friction-free check-ins that set the tone for your event.</h4>
                <p>First impressions matter. Our on-site registration team manages attendee check-in with fast, professional systems that eliminate queues and start your event on the right note. We provide trained staff, badge printing, and real-time attendee tracking so you always know who's in the room.</p>
                <p>Post-event, you receive clean attendance data and reports that feed directly into your follow-up campaigns and ROI calculations — giving you the full picture from registration through to conversion.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="service-button">Get Started</a>
            </div>
        </section>

    </div>
    <CTA />

    <Footer slot="footer" />

</Layout>

<style>
    .page-hero {
        position: relative;
        min-height: 60vh;
        width: 100%;
        overflow: hidden;
        background-image: url('/services-hero.jpg');
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
    }

    .page-hero::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .hero-overlay {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        text-align: center;
        color: #fff;
    }

    .hero-overlay h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-weight: 300;
    }

    .services-intro {
        width: min(85%,1000px);
        margin-inline: auto;
        padding-top: 2rem;
        padding-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .services-intro p {
        color: #333;
    }

    .service-split {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        grid-template-areas:
        "media"
        "text" ;
        gap: 1.25rem;
        align-items: center;
        justify-items: center;
        width: 100%;
        margin-inline: auto;
        padding: 1.5rem 0;
    }

    .service-split .text {
        grid-area: text;
        justify-self: center;
        text-align: center;
        display: grid;
        padding: 1rem;
    }
    .service-split h3 {
        font-size: 2.3rem;
        font-weight: 600;
    }
    .service-image {
        grid-area: media;
        justify-self: center;
        max-width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        width: 340px;
    }

    .service-image img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        display: block;
        border-radius: 14px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }

    .cta {
        width: min(85%, 900px);
        margin-inline: auto;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem 0 3rem;
        display: grid;
        gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        color: #fff;
        background-color: var(--color-dark);
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 0.9rem 1.2rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        transition: filter 0.2s ease;
        font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
        filter: brightness(1.5);
    }

    .text li {
        list-style: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .service-button {
        display: inline-block;
        color: #fff;
        background-color: var(--color-dark);
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 0.9rem 1.2rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        transition: filter 0.2s ease;
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        justify-self: center;
    }

    .service-button:hover {
        filter: brightness(1.5);
    }

    @media (min-width:768px) {
        .service-split {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            grid-template-areas: "text media";
        }

        .service-image {
            justify-self: center;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .service-list > .service-split:nth-child(even) {
            grid-template-areas: "media text";
        }

        .service-list > .service-split:nth-child(even) .service-image {
            justify-self: center;
        }
    }
</style>
